functionCall.arguments: {"query":"SELECT inc_exp_name AS 'Transaction Name', inc_exp_amount AS 'Amount', inc_exp_type AS 'Type', inc_exp_date AS 'Date' FROM income_expense WHERE inc_exp_appId = 10001 AND MONTH(inc_exp_date) = MONTH(CURDATE())-1 AND YEAR(inc_exp_date) = YEAR(CURDATE()) ORDER BY inc_exp_date DESC LIMIT 10","params":[],"chart":{"label": "Transaction Name", "value": "Amount"}}
